txt.en:
'I have a new mission for you, [placeholder].

'My scouts have come back from the High Pass. They could not get to the Misty Mountains, however. It appears the High Pass is protected by a vicious frost-drake! They call her Slátra. They barely avoided her wrath and made it out alive!

'I need you to defeat this vile frost-drake, so that we can continue scouting the mountains.'
Your mission is to defeat the vile drake matron who guards the High Pass.\n\nSpeak to Ausma to travel to the High Pass.
The monster commander in this mission will attempt to summon blizzards.
You have been tasked with dispatching a powerful drake in the High Pass.
Complete Mission: The Matron of the High Pass
DNT - 'When you are ready, my scouts will lead you to the High Pass. I hope that you be able to rid us of that vile drake!'
'Well done! With the matron defeated, we can continue scouting the mountains surrounding the High Pass. The last thing we need is more drakes in these mountains!'
The mission is complete!\n\nSpeak to Ausma for your reward!
Upon the High Pass, a terrible frost drake guards the mountain path….\n\nYour mission is to defeat the vile drake matron who guards the High Pass.
Mission: The Matron of the High Pass
